oys\' School). The school was founded in 1875 by the Worshipful Company of Haberdashers, one of the Great Twelve Livery Companies of the City of London.'], 'question': "Daphne Slater attended what school founded by one of the Great Twelve Livery Company's of the City of London? ", 'reasoning': "Daphne Slater was educated at Haberdashers' Aske's School for Girls, which was founded by the Worshipful Company of Haberdashers. The Worshipful Company of Haberdashers is one of the Great Twelve Livery Companies of the City of London.", 'answer': "Haberdashers' Aske's School for Girls"}) (input_keys=None)]

